      "instruction": "<p>Once the spiced nuts are toasted, chop them roughly (careful they may be hot!)</p><p>Combine<strong> half </strong>the <strong>chopped spiced nuts</strong> (save some for garnish!) with the <strong>orange zest </strong>on a small plate – this is your <strong>spiced nut mix</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>goats' cheese rounds</strong> to the plate and roll, pressing the nuts into the cheese, until fully coated – this is your<strong> rolled goats' cheese</strong></p>",
